reviewText: Classic concert featuring older Disney artists 10th anniversary concert

This was pretty good the music was enjoyable and it had some good singers. i liked most of the artist in the concert like, miley cyrus bowling for soup and the cheetah girls. the others were okay. this is a movie to watch when nothing else is on. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do. kids and adults alike will enjoy it

While I am NOT a Hannah fan, my daughter and all her friends love this stuff. I ordered this at the last minute for a slumber party, and it was a huge hit. Not being a fan, I really did not want to pay too much for this. The price was great and we got it fast.
